import bgImg1 from '../images/background/bg-1.jpg'
import img1 from '../images/common/itemslider.png'

const dataSlider = [
	{
		id: 1,
		title: 'NFT Trading Via Banks',
		desc: 'NFT trading via banks refers to the practice of buying, selling, and trading non-fungible tokens (NFTs) with the involvement of traditional banking institutions',
		img:img1,
		bgImg: bgImg1,
	},
	{
		id: 2,
		title: 'NFT collectionS for everyone',
		desc: 'Nulla ornare sagittis placerat nunc sit tempus enim. Accumsan pellentesque ipsum felis tristique at proin vel turpis.',
		bgImg: bgImg1,
		img: img1,
	},
]

export default dataSlider
